When you&#39;re **serializing** a POJO into JSON if you don&#39;t want to include `null` fields you can make use of the annotation [`@JsonInclude`][include] providing the value of `JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL` or `JsonInclude.Include.NON_EMPTY` (depending on your requirements).

